---
title: Presto Bacon and Mushroom Linguine with Diced Chicken Breast with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Cheese
description: This Presto Bacon and Mushroom Linguine with Diced Chicken Breast is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R203_W02_UK_MB_MODULAR_low-7ace69ae.jpg
